data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!  MOTIVATED SELLERS!!  The lowest priced home in the Golf Course at $682 per sqft!!  Absolutely stunning townhome....impeccably maintained, professionally landscaped and updated 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 1320 sqft townhome located in the highly desirable Key West Golf Course community offers relaxing views of the 5th and 6th golf course holes and lagoon. Situated near the front entrance, it offers preferred convenience for travel in and out of the community. Impressive updates on this larger unit include custom kitchen renovation, wood floors, new front door, composite TREX decking and a screened porch. New stove range and washer/dryer in 2022.  New appliances, gutters and paint in 2019.  This smart home includes the Google Nest automation system including thermostats, lighting and living room fan. On the second floor, both the guest bedroom and primary bedroom have vaulted ceilings. Low monthly HOA fees are $425 and cover cable TV to the home, maintaining the common areas and amenities, and the operation and management of the community. Steps from one of two community heated luxurious swimming pools, a fitness center and 24 hour gated security. Just a short drive to Key West and all the attractions, this home has everything you want and more! Please visit KwgcHoa.com for detailed community association information.
